author: Screen Junkies
description:
It's a bird, it's a plane, it's...a collection of reruns tangentially related to Superman 2025! This week's fresh Honest Trailer has been briefly detained in the phantom zone, but if everything goes according to plan we'll have a new episode for you by the end of the week! In the meantime, rewatch every Superman Honest Trailer we ever made, and try to guess where James Gunn & David Sweaty-Corn's version will rank when we tear into that one like Krypto at a Labubu factory.

0:00 - Superman (1978)
5:01 - Superman IV: The Quest for Peace
8:42 - Superman Returns
12:47 - Man of Steel
16:53 - Batman v Superman
23:45 - Justice League
29:58 - The Snyder Cut

Voice Narration: Jon Bailey the EPIC VOICE GUY (@epicvoiceguy on all socials)

Written by: Spencer Gilbert and Lon Harris
